                <div class="tit_nav">
                    <span class="tit_l">您所在位置：</span><a href="/Home/Index">首页</a><b>></b><span>案例信息</span>
                </div>
                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9635" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-2399</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">798 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“眼看朱楼起，眼看宴宾客，眼看楼塌了”——风控视角看柔宇</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">&quot;Seeing Zhu Lou rising, seeing the banquet guests, seeing the building collapse&quot; - looking at Royole from the perspective of risk control</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">侯志才，袁蓓</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">东华理工大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">深圳市柔宇科技股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">通讯业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">12 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">柔宇科技；柔性显示技术；风险管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Royu Technology; Flexible display technology; Risk management</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">在当今复杂多变的市场环境中，企业的发展面临着来自多方的挑战和威胁，内外部的风险问题日益突出，风险管控在企业经营管理中的地位不断提升，而实施有效的风险管理措施则是企业在市场竞争中站稳脚跟的基石。本案例以柔宇科技成立至破产过程中的风险管控为主线，聚焦柔宇科技从成立之初备受资本宠爱到风险丛生后宣告破产的整个过程，详细阐述了该公司由于创始人重视技术创新而忽略风险管理，决然将公司发展路径由面向企业快速转变成面向消费者，继而出现一系列的经营风险、财务风险和人力资源风险。当风险发生后，企业也并未实施有效的措施进行遏止，而是采用口头向员工承诺报酬、运行仍旧存在缺陷的组织架构等，导致员工罢工、企业资不抵债，最终走向破产结局。这一案例能够帮助学生深入了解风险管理对企业经营的重要性，掌握风险管理是个动态、长期的过程，需要随企业内外部环境变化而变化，并且通过COSO-ERM框架强化风险管理意识，引导学生深入思考和分析，同时也给其他企业特别是科技型企业以风险管理相关借鉴。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In today&#39;s complex and changeable market environment, the development of enterprises is facing challenges and threats from many parties, internal and external risks are becoming increasingly prominent, risk management and control in the operation and management of enterprises continue to improve, and the implementation of effective risk management measures is the cornerstone of enterprises to gain a firm foothold in market competition. This case focuses on the risk management and control from the establishment of Royole Technology to the bankruptcy process, focusing on the entire process of Royole Technology from being favored by capital at the beginning of its establishment to declaring bankruptcy after being full of risks, and elaborating on the company&#39;s rapid transformation of the company&#39;s development path from enterprise-oriented to consumer-oriented due to the founder&#39;s neglect of risk management due to technological innovation, and then a series of operational, financial and human resource risks. When risks occur, companies do not implement effective measures to curb them, but instead use verbal promises of remuneration to employees and organizational structures that are still flawed, resulting in employee strikes, insolvency, and eventually bankruptcy. This case can help students to understand the importance of risk management to business operations, grasp that risk management is a dynamic and long-term process, which needs to change with the changes in the internal and external environment of the enterprise, and strengthen the awareness of risk management through the COSO-ERM framework, guide students to think and analyze deeply, and also provide relevant reference for other enterprises, especially technology-based enterprises.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《风险管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">风险管理的特征；冒险倾向理论；决策理论；风险管理失效；风险类别；风险应对；新风险管理框架</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-06</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
